name: Tindangle Jhrelth
desc: FLIP: You can take 1 Flip monster from your Deck, except “Tindangle Jhrelth”, and either add it to your hand or send it to the GY. If this card is in your hand: You can discard 1 other card from your hand; send 1 “Tindangle” card from your Deck to the GY, except “Tindangle Jhrelth”, also Special Summon this card from your hand in face-down Defense Position. You can only use each effect of "Tindangle Jhrelth" once per turn.
str4: Add the monster to the hand?
